{"tid":742091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳中興慶祝「解禁」照片　員工齊齊舉拇指","createTime":"2018-07-14T09:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T13:11:37.000Z","uid":32938,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"40ffe487672de3db40b98bb45c71f864255589ae","tid":742091,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/170131_93bf46c81f3f619546b76f8ef2f7ed63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F170131_93bf46c81f3f619546b76f8ef2f7ed63.png&h=f1d1df97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨着美國商務部周五（13日）宣布正式對中興通訊解除禁售令，內地社交網流傳相信是中興員工於公司總部大樓內慶祝的照片，相中可見電子告示牌顯示着「解禁了，痛定思痛，再踏征程」等語句。 <br />\n<br />\n在多張網傳照片中，電子告示牌還打出「萬眾一興，堅定信念，迎接黎明的曙光」、「向八萬名員工的堅守家屬的付出致以最真誠的感謝」等語句，另有一班相信為中興員工的男女齊齊豎起拇指合照。 <br />\n<br />\n中興自爆出禁售風波後，於中港兩地股市一度停牌，而復牌後H股股價累跌近六成，A股市值更蒸發近700億元人民幣（約831億港元）。中興前任董事長殷一民曾就事件向股民表示非常愧疚，對不起大家。中興前總裁趙先明曾表示，有信心中興可以很短時間內回復到正常狀態，挽回損失。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/170203_5f0c44d64ac92f461a950582a4088145.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F170203_5f0c44d64ac92f461a950582a4088145.png&h=20d57758&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/170205_71df77e4e0a8d2fe16ec866da8157479.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F170205_71df77e4e0a8d2fe16ec866da8157479.png&h=3cac4d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/170207_f013d4cf7fbe89edf1153641eba3ef4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F170207_f013d4cf7fbe89edf1153641eba3ef4c.png&h=543b1223&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9ee9ae7960891a6f7b63cbf7512f3e1062a0658","tid":742091,"uid":155095,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"201